https://management.azure.com/subscriptions/4b643f6a-df52-44bd-8b8e-b20ea31e75a8/resourceGroups/rg-ccams-qa-use2/providers/Microsoft.DataFactory/factories/adf-ccams-qa-use2-01/queryPipelineRuns?api-version=2018-06-01

Method Field:

Click dropdown and select: POST

Body Field:
Copy and paste this exact body:

{
 "lastUpdatedAfter": "@{adddays(utcnow(),-2)}",
 "lastUpdatedBefore": "@{utcnow()}",
 "filters": [{
  "operand": "PipelineName",
  "operator": "Equals",
  "values": ["Common_Write_to_DB_Pipeline"]
 }]
}

Step 2: Headers Section

Click "+ New" button under Headers
Enter:

Name: Content-Type
Value: application/json



Step 3: Authentication Section

Authentication dropdown: Select Service Principal
Resource field: Enter https://management.azure.com
Tenant field: Enter c7f6413d-1e73-45d2-b0da-a68713b515a7
Service principal ID field: Enter 0cb0296f-4e6c-4470-81de-8d24aae51284

Service Principal Key:

Click dropdown next to Service principal key
Select: Azure Key Vault
Azure Key Vault linked service: Select ls_ccams_kv from dropdown
Secret name field: Enter secret

Step 4: Advanced Settings

Click "Advanced" tab
Timeout: Enter 0.12:00:00
Retry: Enter 0
Retry interval: Enter 30
Leave Secure input and Secure output unchecked

Step 5: Save and Validate

Click empty area of pipeline canvas
Click "Validate" button in top toolbar
Fix any errors shown
Click "Publish all" to save

Follow these exact steps in order. Each field must be filled exactly as specified.
